A revolutionary HRtech and Edtech Startup:
At Empleio, we are passionate about empowering individuals and helping them find employment quickly and effectively. We understand that job hunting can be a challenging task, and the recruitment process can be daunting for applicants. That's why we've developed a unique platform that combines the latest HR technology with educational innovation to provide comprehensive solutions.

What sets us apart?
Smart employment platform: We've created a user-friendly platform that guides applicants through the job-seeking process.

Job search skills training: Our team of human resources experts and professional coaches offer personalized advice and training in job search skills, such as resume writing, interview preparation, and networking strategies.

Specialized training courses: We believe in the power of education to enhance career prospects. That's why we offer specialized training courses to improve our users' skills and knowledge, giving them a competitive edge in today's job market.

Labor market updates: We keep our users informed about the latest labor market trends and demands.

User-centered experience: Our primary goal is to simplify the job search process for our users. We actively listen to feedback and suggestions from our community and continuously improve our platform to provide the best possible experience.

At Empleio, we believe that everyone has talent and deserves fair opportunities to advance their career. That's why we are committed to equity and diversity in the workplace. So, if you're looking for a job, join Empleio and discover how we can assist you.

18.description:
Cumbi is a revolutionary platform that transforms the landscape of cross-border payments, enabling individuals and businesses to effortlessly receive digital dollars and convert them into local currency. Designed to dismantle the technical and financial complexities of blockchain technology, Cumbi offers a range of solutions tailored to different needs. 

For individuals, it provides a quick, secure way to receive digital dollars and have them directly deposited into their bank accounts in local currency. Businesses benefit from an all-in-one platform for accepting global payments in digital dollars, with automatic conversion to local currency, expanding their market reach. 

E-commerce platforms can easily integrate Cumbi's payment gateway to accept international payments in real-time, eliminating hidden fees and exchange rate concerns. Additionally, Cumbi offers an API solution for web3 companies, enabling their users to withdraw funds in local currency and creating an additional revenue stream for our partners.

12.short_description: Clooned is a digital marketing tool that helps businesses to create 360-degree, 3D products and no-app required AR/VR experiences.

18.description:
3D is becoming a new media standard. And we believe that, it creates a new and fresh category in communication and marketing.

Clooned is an SaaS start up focused on the online capabilities of 3D files, for different needs such as sales, marketing, customer support and many more.
We specialize in creating web-based 3D technology, with a focus on sectors and today's needs.

With Clooned's online service, users can easily create a digital online copy of their 3D product models or spaces, and then use them in variety of ways, including on 360-degree web browser tours, in Augmented Reality (AR), and in Virtual Reality (VR).

One of the key benefits of Clooned's technology is that it eliminates the need for users to download a separate app in order to view 3D models on devices, also with AR or VR. Instead, users can simply access the models through a web browser, making it easy to share and collaborate on 3D projects with others.

Clooned's technology meets the diverse needs of a wide variety of industries, from maritime to defense industry, from architecture to machinery.
